article.description: — Traci Carter had 19 points and nine rebounds as Hartford topped New Hampshire 69-57 on Wednesday night.
article.headline: Carter scores 19 to lead Hartford over New Hampshire 69-57
article.linkText: Carter scores 19 to lead Hartford over New Hampshire 69-57
article.story: WEST HARTFORD, Conn. -- — Traci Carter had 19 points and nine rebounds as Hartford topped New Hampshire 69-57 on Wednesday night. Austin Williams had 18 points and six rebounds for Hartford (3-10, 1-0 America East Conference). David Shriver added 12 points. Marco Foster had 14 points for the Wildcats (6-6, 1-2). Qon Murphy added 12 points. Blondeau Tchoukuiegno had 10 points and nine rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
